  },
  "content": "This is a fixture document used to prove the mif-to-pdf skill embeds every MIF frontmatter field into the produced PDF's metadata.\n\nIt has a real body with two paragraphs, so the converter's text-wrapping and pagination get exercised, not just the metadata path.\n\nA third paragraph checks that multi-paragraph bodies render as separate blocks rather than one run-on line."
